  lines:
  - speakerName: Lil B.A.H
    dialogueText: Yo, wassup bro? This the PC spot, right?
  - speakerName: Shopkeeper
    dialogueText: "Yeah man, welcome. What you lookin\u2019 for?"
  - speakerName: Lil B.A.H
    dialogueText: "Aight, so\u2026 I\u2019m tryna build a fire PC."
  - speakerName: Lil B.A.H
    dialogueText: "Somethin\u2019 crazy fast.\nI be makin\u2019 music, streamin\u2019,
      maybe some games too."
  - speakerName: Shopkeeper
    dialogueText: whats ur budget?
  - speakerName: Lil B.A.H
    dialogueText: "I just want it lookin\u2019 expensive and fast as hell."
  - speakerName: Shopkepper
    dialogueText: You know anything about PCs?
  - speakerName: Shopkepper
    dialogueText: "Got you. I\u2019ll build you somethin\u2019 clean and powerful."
